features: Binding & Cover Design: A newest combination of thread and glue offers you a LAYING FLAT and sturdier binding to write in comfortably. A hard cardboard vegan leather cover makes it DURABLE to get knocked around in travel and RIGID to jot down notes on hands.

Quality & Number of Pages: FOUNTAIN PEN FRIENDLY paper is smooth and perfectly reliable, resisting feathering and bleedthrough. Cream-colored acid free paper is a little more soothing to the eye. 172 NUMBERED pages with 3 table of contents for quick reference.

Sheet Style & Size: 7mm Spacing medium (college) ruled keeps writings neat without being as strict. 5.7" x 8.4" Journal is perfect for slipping into a bag or backpack while giving you plenty of room for writing down your ideas,thoughts in one page.

Outstanding Details: Designed with elastic band closure, 2 colored ribbon bookmarks, expandable pockets inside the cover for loose leaf paper, sticker labels for classifying each notebook, elastic pen loop for pen accessible.
Reliable Writing Partner: Professional design + high quality material + sophisticated production creates you a unique journal notebook for diary, notes, planner, thoughts and keep them forever.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Hardcover Writing Notebook Crafted with the highest quality materials, this notebook features a sturdy hardcover that will provide extra protection for the pages, which can help prevent bending, tearing, and other damage. This can be especially beneficial if you plan on using the notebook for a long period of time, or if you want to preserve your notes for future reference.Writing Surface: The hardcover provides a sturdy writing surface, which can be more comfortable and conducive to good penmanship. And thread bound offers 180° laying flat.Customization: Hardcover notebooks can be customized with a variety of cover materials, designs, and embellishments, allowing you to create a notebook that truly reflects your style and personality.

Numbered Pages Thick Paper Notebook Standout features of this notebook is its numbered pages, which makes organizing and finding your notes a breeze. Never again will you waste time flipping through pages trying to locate that one important piece of information. Plus, the pages are made with premium paper that is thick and durable, allowing you to use a variety of pens and markers without fear of bleeding through or smudging.College ruled paper help make writing neat and organized, perfect for planner layout, diary, journaling and notes taking.

A convenient elastic closure to keep your notes secure A handy elastic pen loop to keep your pen accessible 2 colors ribbon bookmarks to pick up right where you left off. And with its sleek, minimalist design, this notebook is perfect for both personal and professional use.

5.5 x 8.5 Notebook, Half Letter Size With its compact A5 size, this notebook is portable enough to take with you anywhere, whether you're heading to a meeting, lecture, or just jotting down your daily to-do list. Whether you're a student, a professional, or just someone who loves to write, the A5 Hardcover Notebook with Numbered Pages is the perfect tool for capturing your thoughts and ideas. Order yours today and experience the ultimate in note-taking convenience and quality!

reviews.reviewText: As I get older...i tend to forget things!I tried using Field Notes to keep track of various things. I carried one for medical info, I had one for quick notes and a 3rd to keep info on different vendors I've used for family parties etc. Although Field Notes are small, carrying 3 was getting ridiculous.This leather journal is perfect. I am using post it notes to divide the journal into 3 sections. It's one of the smoothest paper I've ever written on and I'm pretty particular.I also find it easier to take notes at the dr with a bigger notebook.
